1.copy autoload doc plugin to ~/.vim for Linux and $vim/vimfiles for Windows
2.execute :helptags ~/.vim/doc for Linux and :helptags $/vim/vimfiles/doc for Windows
3.install ctags if not exist
4.copy _vimrc to ~/ for Linux and rename it as .vimrc; copy _vimrc to $HOMEPATH$ for Windows
5.totorseGit:modified
